# Expense Operating Depreciation Property Plant And Equipment Amount

## identifier
de7501

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, of depreciation charged to profit and loss in respect of property, plant and equipment as determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.DepreciationPropertyPlantAndEquipment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
